(17, 7, '配送费收取标准', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">北京区域</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">配送政策:</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">运费说明：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">六环内</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 订单金额满500元，免配送费；（不含上楼费）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 订单金额低于500元，每单收取39元运费。（不含上楼费）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">六环外</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">订单金额超过2000元，免运费（不含上楼费），不足2000元每单配送费100元（不含远郊区县）。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><br />\r\n</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">远郊区县(包含密云、延庆、怀柔、顺义、门头沟、燕郊、固安等地）以六环为界限</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">，按</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">实际里程收取运费5元/公里。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">订单配送特别说明：</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">（1）每笔订单只有一个送货地址，不可兼送多处。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="co