楼等</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">3、如因客户未告知实情包括</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">但</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">不限于货到时不能进电梯，不能进小区，现场与客户确认订单时</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">与</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">告知的距离不相符，现场产生的人工搬</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">运</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">费由客户承担。（运费100元/次，上楼费收费标准同上表&nbsp;）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">4.辅料上楼摆放标准：可按工长要求标准摆放</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">5.其余未尽事宜，可与客服联系</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0pt"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p><span style="color: #000000">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="15" style="font-family: ''Hiragino Sans GB''; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13.5pt; font-weight: bold; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><font face="宋体">四、</font>全国物流配送收费标准：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 19.2pt; text-indent: 0pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial"><span style="color: #000000"><img alt="" width="573" height="598" src="/images/upload/Image/12121(1).png" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>\r\n<p><span id="1468311853549E" style="display: none">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1242577041, '', 0, 'http://', ''),
(82, 10, '支付流程', '<p style="text-align: center"><strong>点击&ldquo;去结算&rdquo;进入支付页面</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><img alt="" style="width: 1091px; height: 368px" src="/images/upload/Image/33333333(2).png" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong>设置收货信息，选择支付方式，填写发票信息提交支付</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><img alt="" style="width: 918px; height: 635px" src="/images/upload/Image/3333333333(2).png" /></strong></p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1465240262, '', 0, 'http://', '支付流程'),
(83, 10, '货到付款', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0pt"><span style="font-size: large">货到付款：选择货到付款，在订单送达时您可选择现金、POS机刷卡方式支付货款，在订单未妥投之前您还可以进入&ldquo;我的订单&rdquo;在线支付货款。</span></div>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img width="425" height="387" alt="" src="/images/upload/Image/20188662.jpg" /></p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1465240286, '', 0, 'http://', '货到付款'),
(84, 10, '在线支付', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="margin: 0pt"><span style="font-size: large">在线支付：选择在线支付，请您进入&ldquo;我的订单&rdquo;，点击&ldquo;付款&rdquo;，按提示进行操作；目前在线支付支持财付通、微信扫码、在线余额等方式进行支付，可根据您的使用喜好进行选择</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">。</span></div>', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1465240459, '', 0, 'http://', '在线支付'),
(85, 10, '发票问题', '<div><span style="font-size: large"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">网站所售商品都是正品，均开具正规发票，发票金额含配送费金额，另有说明的除外。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: large"><b><span class="15" style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">1.</span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">如何获得增值税普通发票：</span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">下单时选择<font face="Arial">&ldquo;增值税</font><font face="宋体">普通发票</font><font face="Arial">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">自助开取，此发票可用作单位报销凭证，一个订单对应一张或多张发票，不同的物流中心发出的包裹开具不同的发票，发票会随每次</font></span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">订单</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">一同发出。</span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: large"><b><span class="15" style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">2</span></b><b><span class="15" style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)">.<font face="宋体">如何获得增值税专用发票：</font></span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">下单时选择<font face="Arial">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">增值税专用发票 </font><font face="Arial">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">自助开取。首次开具增值税专用发票的顾客，需要提供加盖公章的</font><font face="Arial">&nbsp;①营业执照（副本）文件复印件（扫描盖章）</font><font face="宋体"> </font><font face="Arial">②</font><font face="宋体">一般纳税人资格证书或认定文件复印件（扫描盖章），填写资质信息后选择上传资质证件扫描件，收到您的开票资料后，会尽快审核。注意：有效增值税开票资质仅为一个。（要求订单满3000元以上）</font></span></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: large"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(255,255,255); letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255); mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"><font face="宋体">开票信息示例：</font></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img alt="" src="/images/upload/Image/11111111111111111111111(1).png" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-size: large">绿优全装开票信息专用邮箱：&nbsp; </span></span><a href="mailto:lyqz365@lyqz365.com"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-size: large">lyqz365@lyqz365.com</span></span></a></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-size: large">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-size: large">如有其他需求请致电：400-6038-365</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="font-size: large"><img alt="" width="788" height="352" src="/images/upload/Image/12123.png" /></span></span></p>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: large"><!--EndFragment--></span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1465240523, '', 0, 'http://', '发票问题'),
(71, 6, '售后政策', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1465238448, '', 0, 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` (`article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description`) VALUES
(73, 6, '退货说明', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">一 、</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">承诺：自用户收到商品之日起（以</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">签收单或</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">快递面单签收时间为准），按以下标准提供退换货服务：</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">1) 　</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">7</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">天内无理由退货，因质量问题退货的来回运费由</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">承担，因非质量问题（</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">买错、不需求</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">）退货的来回运费由客户承担；</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">2)　无论是那种情况的退货，请您先垫付运费，</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">将会根据您选择的退款方式将运费和商品差价一并退还给您。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">3)　符合退货要求的订单，不要用平邮方式寄回，不支持到付。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">二、退货时务必将货品连同外包装以及相关附件（</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">包装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">袋、 包装塑料纸、发货单单等等）一并寄回，且务必按照要求填写退换货单，否则将会影响我们为您处理退换货的速度。&nbsp;</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">三、注明退货原因，如果商品存在质量问题，请务必说明；</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">五、收到用户寄回的商品后，我们将在3个工作日内为您办理退货。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">六、以下情况不予办理退货：</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(1)　任何非</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">官方网站出售的商品；</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(2)　因非正常使用或保管不当导致出现质量问题的商品(包括但不限于：用锋利的物品把商品划伤，因放置于高温物体旁引起的变形等)</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">七、 促销活动的产品，需按活动规则办理退货。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold">退换货流程</span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><img alt="" style="width: 847px; height: 120px" src="/images/upload/Image/12123(1).png" /></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold">退款方式</span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(1)　预存款退款，将退款金额直接退回到您的</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">绿优全装</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">预存款账户中。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(2)　支付宝&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;财付通&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;快钱&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;银联退款，退款金额会以即时到帐的方式打入您提供的相应账号中。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(3)　银行账号退款，请您提供接收退款的银行 信息，包括开户行名称、银行账号、账户名，退款金额将会在3个工作日内打入您提供的银行账号中</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">(4)　如果所支付的订单中含有非现金部分（如优惠券、积分等），在退款时，非现金部分不能折现，将以原形式退回。</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold">售后咨询</span></b><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">若有任何售后问题，请发送邮件至：</span><a href="http://www.qqqiyemail.com/"><u><span style="color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: underline; text-underline: single">http://www.qqqiyemail.com</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal"><br />\r\n</span></u></a></div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="font-size: x-small"><span style="color: #ff0000">注：商城系统在完善更新阶段，如有换货情况订单请走退货申请流程</span></span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">退货地址：北京市大兴区青云店镇工业区敬业路1号敬业达建材</span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">邮编：102605</span></div>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">收货人：赵文博</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0pt"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">联系方式</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 11pt; font-weight: normal">：010-51665803</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0pt">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1465238481, '', 0, 'http://', ''),
