so-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">三、安全性</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">无论您是电话订购商品或是网络订购商品，我们会保证交易信息的安全。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">四、隐私权</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />\r\n</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">绿优全装网上</span><span style="text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: ''yes''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">商城尊重您的隐私权，在任何情况下，我们都不会将您的个人和订单信息出售或泄露给任何第三方（国家司法机关调取除外）。我们从网站上或电话中得到的所有客户信息仅用来处理您的相关订单。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p" style="padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 16.5pt; marg